results.title: Live, Laugh, Love Badge Reel
results.description:
PLEASE READ FULL DESCRIPTION BEFORE PURCHASING
This is a listing for a 2-inch Badge Reel
Badge Reels will come with a matching snap bead
The acrylic has a layer of shimmery glitter on the back. It is then sealed with a smooth layer of epoxy for durability and shine.
Acrylics are made of 1/8” cast clear acrylic, high quality polyester glitter (color will not fade over time), and epoxy.
Acrylics are permanently adhered to a clear swivel retractable alligator clip or belt clip that extends to 35”.
*Avoid prolonged exposure to high temperatures
*Avoid dropping on hard surfaces
Wipe clean with a dry lint-free cloth
..

What happens if my badge reel breaks?

I am not responsible for any damages to an item after 90 days of delivery. I will not refund, nor send a replacement after 90 days. You will have to place a new order.
If after the 90 days your badge reel breaks from the reel holder, apply a generous portion of E6000 glue, or any form of super glue to the back of the acrylic and adhere to reel holder. Let dry for 48 hours before usage.



BUYER is RESPONSIBLE for Correct Shipping Address and Personalization. 
I will ship all packages to address provided
I will personalize items (which have those options) as it is written. Example: if you send a personalization in all CAPITAL LETTERS YOU WILL RECEIVE YOUR ITEM IN ALL CAPITAL LETTERS. Misspelling is the buyer’s responsibility. I will not replace an item because it was typed in the box incorrectly. Seller is NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR INCORRECT ADDRESSES WHICH WERE GIVEN: Once it is shipped seller is not responsible for duration of travel to address. I have no control of the trucks, planes, trains and automobiles in which they are in the transfer / destination process. 


I use the best quality of badge reels as possible!!!
The lifespan of a Badge Reel determines on the wear and tear use. If pulling on the extension cord excessively and hard may result in popping. Sometimes the badge reel could pop open without any reason. There is no such thing as a 100% perfect quality. Although, I do use a high standard quality; I have seen them just break, (sometimes it just a faulty reel). I will replace the badge reel if this happens. Please send me photo. If it is the acrylic which pops off only, apply a small amount of e 6000 glue or any super glue to the back of acrylic and place it back onto the badge reel. Let dry for at least 24-48 hours. 
I have seen this happen when badge reel is dropped / knocked / banged repletely and excessive pressure placed onto the acrylic with placement 
Badges are not made to hold an excessive amount of weight, Examples: Pens, small hand sanitizer bottle, flashlight (pen light size). The weight of these items can and will decrease the longevity of your badge reel and it will break.
Dropping Your Acrylic Badge Reel or Banging against hard surfaces may cause it to break.
Handle with Care. When attach your badge reel to clothing, don’t apply pressure directly onto the acrylic piece, may result in popping off the acrylic.

results.title: Gift for couples. 1 price for 2.  Leather Bracelet Laser Engraved Quote Personalized Customized Personal Custom Leather Wrap Cuff Wide  B006
results.description:
Double strand wrap leather bracelet, made of high quality genuine leather. Wraps two times around the wrist to create a modern urban look. Beautiful natural colors. Optional metal charm buckle which says "Live Laugh Love." The words on the charm cannot be customized. 

It's a simple, yet modern urban look. Adjustable to fit wrist sizes from roughly 5 to 7.5 inches (13 to 19 cm).  Total length = 16.5", Width = 1/2" 

You can have any saying you want engraved on this bracelet. Popular requests include names, places, religious quotes, famous quotes... whatever you want! We can also do different languages. This is a wonderful personalized gift for someone you love, including yourself. The laser engraver works by burning the surface of the item. Therefore, the engraving will be very subtle on the darker colors, and stands out best on the Caramel Tan, Berry Pink, Cracked White, and Cracked Teal. 

Our Cracked colors are made from a flexible split leather, and are finished with a crackly color paint on the outside. All other colors are made from vegetable-tanned leather. 

{{ How to Order }} We have three standard options: #A) The word "Love" in different languages. #B) The quote: You can't get to where you are except for where you've been. Love the life you live. Live the life you love. #C) If you want to engrave your own personalized quote: The bracelet will fit a maximum of about 90 characters (spaces included) per strand. That is 180 characters total. Double check that spelling, punctuation, and spaces are EXACTLY how you want them, because we copy and paste from your note. Unless otherwise requested, your message will only be engraved one time on the bracelet, and the phrase will not be repeated
